  "texts": [
    "Ac-cording to Zhou et al. (2022), the Xiong'an railway station in China was successfully built us-ing a variety of smart construction techniques, including AI, CC, and BIM technology, in order to achieve self-sufficiency in lighting energy and real-time building management.",
    "Taken togeth-er, previous studies on AI in CC technology for construction energy efficiency have reported potential results.",
    "According to the studies, the use of AI and CC technologies can significantly improve energy efficiency in the CI by employing a variety of cutting-edge strategies, including intelligent traffic control systems, smart construction methods, and energy-sensitive system frameworks.",
    "In the CI, AI and CC have become transformative technologies that present new opportunities to boost sustainability, productivity, and safety.",
    "There is still work to be done to completely realize the potential of AI and CC in applications related to construction, even though a growing body of research has explored these topics."
  ]
}